Problem: Given the right triangles ABC and ABD, what is the length of segment BC, in units? [asy]
size(150);
pair A, B, C, D, X;
A=(0,0);
B=(0,12);
C=(-16,0);
D=(-35,0);
draw(A--B--D--A);
draw(B--C);
draw((0,1.5)--(-1.5,1.5)--(-1.5,0));
label("$37$", (B+D)/2, NW);
